text:
Good job.
...If there's anything you noticed.

Ah, no, there were no problems at all.
It was really good.

But if I had to point out something... let's see...
Your smile might have been the most memorable part.
...In a good way? Or a bad way?

Huh?
Oh, of course in a good way!

...I see, that's a relief.
If that's enough to get a good evaluation.

...Of course, if you have an even better smile,
I'd love to see it someday.

I won't show you.
Definitely not to you.
